high_descs: Go forward to the dresser.
Pick up the pencil on the far left of the dresser.
Turn around and go to the desk.
Put the pencil on the desk.
Turn around and go back to the dresser.
Pick up the pencil from the middle of the dresser.
Return to the desk.
Put the pencil to the left of the first pencil on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put two pencils on the desk.

high_descs: Walk slightly to the left and then turn to the right to walk towards the filing cabinet and the box.
Get the yellow pencil under the brown tape on the filing cabinet.
Walk to your right, make a right turn at the end of the room and walk straight to the desk.
Put the pencil on top of the desk, in front of the tape next to the lap top.
Turn around and go back to the filing cabinet.
get another yellow pencil from the filing cabinet.
Go to the right and turn right to walk back to the desk.
Put the pencil in front of the second tape on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put 2 pencils in front of the brown tape on the desk with a chair.

high_descs: Walk over to the green dresser.
Pick up the yellow pencil on the left side of the dresser.
Turn and go past the window to the desk.
Set the pencil on the front edge of the desk.
Turn and go back to the green dresser.
Pick up the yellow pencil to the left of the disk.
Turn and go past the window to the desk.
Set the pencil down on the desk in front of the clock on the left.
anns.task_desc: Put two pencils on the desk.
